      "file_path": "main/src/main/java/org/onap/policy/pap/main/rest/PolicyComponentsHealthCheckProvider.java",
      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 100,
      "message": "shouldn't do this - because the factory is a singleton, it will impact anything else using managed HttpClients",
