      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 98,
      "message": "Hi Jim,\n\nOK, thanks for the information. Maybe we can just use regular sequence call since we only have clients to call. Or any other suggestion to make it better?\n\nI agree, we should rework on all usages of HttpClientFactory.",
