      "line": 100,
      "message": "I agree. It tried to fix the problem of repeating calling to getHttpClients. It does not work well.\nPolicyComponentsHealthCheckProvider is created per request. \nhttps://git.onap.org/policy/pap/tree/main/src/main/java/org/onap/policy/pap/main/rest/PolicyComponentsHealthCheckControllerV1.java#n85",
      "author": {
